  "text": "Location of mutated residues on the ENaC surface. To estimate the location of the mutated residues on the ENaC surface, we mapped the positions of the homologous residues on the structure of ASIC1 [CITATION_1] . Figure 12 shows the surface positions of four residues homologous to ␣-ENaC R350, D393, D400, and D446 (K247, D290, D297, and T337 in ASIC1).",
